 changes efficiently, ensuring everything aligns well with the new approach. Let’s get started with that edit!", "thinkingSignature": "{\"id\":\"rs_05bb549048ace4550169f4edf3b14c8195a6e21d081e057003\",\"type\":\"reasoning\",\"encrypted_content\":\"gAAAAABp9O4zV1kE7OpWSbFzKaJ57pLb-9OTPSnDWSMa4Vi1w9sZk4PHyNypiQdGZI_MRYrveeo_dLQiTw8JEdPhVBrocrmMgRVHWANOPqOwSASguokTeqlK6StCGJ7sH2RL2b4K-qVOYki9xlUFqIVnmvYYlDQgbhtvS8121UNdqJpXqVI_hnZcedp9eicUOA02i0dVjn4Jf9pT4D4Q2L1kIBYpo1uUHh_cMs98R04XroKHnLEFcHdCaqmCUXXGztcJ96XtVJxvfKKKz1J76H280OQU57oYZB90Ezk9cRvF7jzKaAGzW59VEyTMJ9gitQpgQmvBt91kSTSIyi4pym2AyCjXcxRlZhMjCbgqnS9Js3S4CvqpnJV1d7oozbaNqS2earVNX7LHV0To_kwFHA6mXDHkdFs7WlH8ujbs1mSpf2UHKZUtOpYWvAdQfLx1s9j9TS09z2Lgj9eMDsw9BfO8Au-DADlyrII3NpaiMhuXb-Si4U4BJHODYdT1oPuwnpAI0DiTJ4rLczjVMIIwJCPo5nIvxI3rHQTlsBy2hancK8-HLm_XZQyW63rwj7r0r72Ap5W2oVjI5JyAzZTcYmD96iihqpJhyVDqa_eQ2SSfbD73qe-ZVtfIP2lYNyvkwCCauP6bjSoH0gRtZgWb1SYBhJTb4m_K_SUUoec9NyLkoxWXq009hY823qpabH1cEKg0vOrIvNOOZK76SWIv2OelCCdJEMSfuzF7G8zPUWmS4EDUv5k6iSU9odNYwul-fkaUbDRYrM3PxiXY74iPUbNgOgYvaC8HPjTTV9ncmZcclgW9J16YZ1vCUwxZQ3Fox9Ezp0227FfFJ9M3pxCelQkU_Xz5qcWh8oDqinPYgNRBmtB6ntQxn0zgH30snZHCs4wkDLMxawTzvnDdo61hZe6Hmz-rfr1timDcwi1KzvwwhniE9ZjgaaXgJMSuIK_btX1qnIhFdN_K8tPZUJJqC58aaSAAL54VGzBoFnVfbc5LLLLqyEc3WarUu3GCf0f9yMdewKmQbUVh1iwxWvJBFJV4vV8iD63fQPDwJLKyhKL9bOdIJkwp0oWFjAmyEEnRMa_J9Uh3s7B5edn56zCxBLMg9E2GpU_NHsKm3V-wxQJpt7tHarQkLmmm8RUs_2G-GeEkuLzYpVhGlFdRs8TO0iab6Pi-j7Cif09YYYWwg22Zd4wmNsSOcHqFxw3JIczqA1Em_ipnKMonLT9oP8FL5iqcSvfokxfNqdpTmrVnDreCaGSYdwXcDGgnM-v7eXm2nvTHMxLHoQU6osCAz8Bf8mzvB3RO2XZvfznub6YbbUjoJW4dDvacwWWWd8od3zq6d9_ytIlq1ZYIXy5fPxE6l-ceSB48khHn_T758RvgknqphxEnGqwMtrRS-vbTey8SQMMIMPQJq1IyXEPxFkL9dk9OnomCqU_ufrHFhUwLf_DnRAdAZk3cF6IXrVIYrqhTJwTXhVwgi9NG5bFP7wChX3RjU9CEkXDd9a_ES2bsJ6Lhtw6lDJ-J3_TE0jSmHkVNMh29iJzGi3wGUlEmhh6bboNZWBQQdDb0JOQiednZsMuVwoD_4igTpQ_sZFnJvAIc6JMc1ztsTnfRThzqTWgPDeNY44KO2xgMntkRx4uKmeXOHVRhgsA9f8F5mpClEAkkauF-fE75eCsgwzRl8GC7S75bveuA7KVjn-S10mEwPR44hT0z7V0gI3d1NSZ3LsNo8ChkKc76SnNrLuUv0OA-zg58